---
import PageLayout from "@/layouts/Base.astro";

const meta = {
	description: "Research - Suraj Sahu",
	title: "Research",
};
---

<PageLayout meta={meta}>
	<h1 class="title mb-12">Research</h1>
	<div class="prose prose-sm prose-cactus max-w-none">
		<div class="mb-12">
			<h2 class="mb-4 text-xl">Research Overview</h2>
			<p class="mb-4 text-justify">
				My research lies at the intersection of computational physics, biophysics, and developmental biology.
				I develop and apply computational models to understand how physical interactions at the cellular level
				give rise to complex multicellular structures and networks. My work focuses on uncovering the fundamental
				principles of self-organization in biological systems, particularly in the context of vascular network formation.
			</p>
		</div>

		<div class="mb-12">
			<h2 class="mb-4 text-xl">Research Interests</h2>
			<ul class="list-inside list-disc space-y-2">
				<li>
					<strong>Computational Biophysics:</strong> Using physics-based computational models to understand
					biological phenomena
				</li>
				<li>
					<strong>Self-Organization:</strong> Investigating how order emerges from local interactions in
					living systems
				</li>
				<li>
					<strong>Vascular Development:</strong> Modeling blood vessel formation and remodeling during
					embryonic development
				</li>
				<li>
					<strong>Cell-ECM Interactions:</strong> Understanding how cells interact with and remodel their
					extracellular matrix environment
				</li>
				<li>
					<strong>Multicellular Networks:</strong> Studying the formation, structure, and function of
					multicellular networks
				</li>
				<li>
					<strong>Statistical Mechanics of Living Systems:</strong> Applying statistical physics principles
					to biological systems
				</li>
			</ul>
		</div>

		<div class="mb-12">
			<h2 class="mb-4 text-xl">Current Projects</h2>
			<div class="space-y-6">
				<div>
					<h3 class="mb-2 font-semibold">Computational Modeling of Vascular Network Formation</h3>
					<p class="text-sm opacity-90">
						Developing agent-based and continuum models to simulate the formation of blood vascular networks
						during embryonic development. This work integrates cellular mechanics, chemical signaling, and
						tissue-scale remodeling to understand how functional vascular patterns emerge.
					</p>
				</div>
				<div>
					<h3 class="mb-2 font-semibold">Physical Principles of Self-Organization</h3>
					<p class="text-sm opacity-90">
						Investigating the universal physical principles that govern self-organization in multicellular
						systems. This includes studying how cells coordinate their behavior through mechanical and
						chemical cues to form stable, functional structures.
					</p>
				</div>
				<div>
					<h3 class="mb-2 font-semibold">Cell-ECM Mechanobiology</h3>
					<p class="text-sm opacity-90">
						Examining the bidirectional interactions between cells and their extracellular matrix,
						particularly how mechanical forces influence cell behavior and how cells remodel their
						mechanical environment.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="mb-12">
			<h2 class="mb-4 text-xl">Publications</h2>
			<p class="mb-4 text-sm opacity-75">
				For a complete list of publications, please visit my
				<a
					class="cactus-link"
					href="https://scholar.google.com/citations?user=sFKtiyQAAAAJ&hl=en&authuser=1"
					target="_blank"
					rel="noopener"
				>
					Google Scholar profile
				</a>.
			</p>
		</div>

		<div class="mb-12">
			<h2 class="mb-4 text-xl">Collaborations</h2>
			<p class="mb-4">
				I collaborate with experimental and computational groups working on:
			</p>
			<ul class="list-inside list-disc space-y-1">
				<li>Developmental biology and tissue morphogenesis</li>
				<li>Mechanobiology and mechanochemical signaling</li>
				<li>Complex systems and network science</li>
				<li>Soft matter physics and active matter</li>
			</ul>
		</div>

		<div class="mb-12">
			<h2 class="mb-4 text-xl">Methods & Tools</h2>
			<div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2">
				<div>
					<h3 class="mb-2 font-semibold">Computational Approaches</h3>
					<ul class="list-inside list-disc text-sm">
						<li>Agent-based modeling</li>
						<li>Continuum mechanics</li>
						<li>Statistical physics</li>
						<li>Network analysis</li>
						<li>Numerical simulations</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
				<div>
					<h3 class="mb-2 font-semibold">Programming & Software</h3>
					<ul class="list-inside list-disc text-sm">
						<li>Python (NumPy, SciPy, NetworkX)</li>
						<li>C/C++</li>
						<li>High-performance computing</li>
						<li>Data analysis & visualization</li>
						<li>Machine learning tools</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</PageLayout>
